{"tid":1503210,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"整個英文youtube作為宣揚渠道比外國知？","createTime":"2019-08-25T01:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T14:31:04.000Z","uid":76310,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b5e0c854962b092aa31e7c9497f46e97d1c74692","tid":1503210,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:26:13.000Z","msg":"不如整個英文youtube做宣揚<br />\n每星期，不，每日都總發生一些事情<br />\n然後這些事情不止一件，而且當中包括許多人和事，仲有各式各樣的不平<br />\n每天每刻向外國文宣，要推要做宣傳得辛苦<br />\n做個youtube綜合所有<br />\n不但方便大家，也方便外媒，也讓外國易於跟進所有野<br />\nYoutube也是現在常用宣傳手法<br />\n有沒有文宣手足group做？"},{"pid":"de3268d4628c01d9a39d0a2b2a37a1f8798b4ca8","tid":1503210,"uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:35:46.000Z","msg":"而且頻道做得受歡迎有收入<br />\n外國人也易跟進香港所有事<br />\n每天也發生很多事 太多枝節 開個youtube總結是最好不過"},{"pid":"f3a76782d5a71659713119d2d062a8a0492d0a75","tid":1503210,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:37:57.000Z","msg":"例如<br />\n21/7有上環和元朗二單野<br />\n只是講元朗，黑警，黑社會，市民，示威者，4方面講已經有排講<br />\n上環又可以分開講"},{"pid":"8ab7a290c2fe00cb0542dbeb29ac520d1adb3512","tid":1503210,"uid":196855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a2ab44b11380d7b7faa13ac53f0b2e867a6680","tid":1503210,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:39:04.000Z","msg":"而且做youtube可以幫大家總結發生過什麼事<br />\n當中的細節和枝節也不會成為歷史被遺忘"},{"pid":"496325cfa760ce3825e296ce6e03aeb42479116e","tid":1503210,"uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:40:31.000Z","msg":"剛剛想一想，除了英文，方便外國勢力，作為香港人，應該紀錄我地走過的路<br />\n因為是長期抗爭，想紀錄我地的心路歷程"},{"pid":"587919862e60131ba700f5321171fd8b9ba077ef","tid":1503210,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:42:56.000Z","msg":"有冇人聯絡英文好的文宣組<br />\n叫佢地合作整個平台講下抗爭運動中所有的人與事<br />\n以後做文宣方便好多<br />\n外國傳媒和外國政府可以輕易知道發生什麼事<br />\n而且不會因為紅色傳媒沒有報導，就遺留很多人和事"},{"pid":"c79c1a22a9157f8aaae0a71f94cfa083f3bf80b9","tid":1503210,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:44:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07f83b70de7ce2cd502b55b324db2f0e050b5327","tid":1503210,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:45:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月1 (日) 一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">9月14中秋,未必CALL 到人, 所以</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月6 (六), 9 月7(日) 連續2日一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">之後既每個星期六/日 要起碼有一日一定係機場</span></span>"},{"pid":"94ce9c3e779ee4f418633cd9abc25b9fe26c436e","tid":1503210,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:47:00.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n有冇人推比文宣組知<br />\n一個中一個英"},{"pid":"446cd6e4d8a8db2958b8197c9069fada5681f9e0","tid":1503210,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:55:13.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n推到比文宣組睇"},{"pid":"b460a71fd897e3f46fed3c323d3761dab840f604","tid":1503210,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:04:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0c8ff0c84247a291d2ffd3fcba96f89304725fb","tid":1503210,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:07:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20849141c0c7eeff6054eba5a97359c723842281","tid":1503210,"uid":283136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:08:24.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n（尋谷）就快開學 有冇巴絲可以開個老豆搵狗囝嘅谷？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1503197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1503197</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2caf36832c3cdf98d5d5754eea5c2b2b3f67b4db","tid":1503210,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:29:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c1947563c6dd7a5331e7